79
00:03:47,759 --> 00:03:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] A ne, ne, ne, čili.

80
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:50,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, pod stresom.

81
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,520
