96
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:40,879
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ja.

97
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:46,959
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zato je promijenio sve moje predrasude u vezi njega.

98
00:04:47,439 --> 00:04:49,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ne, ti si uletio, jako sam i bio strašan.

99
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:51,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bože, sam i bio strašan.

100
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:55,199
