158
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:30,959
[SPEAKER_01] Ali mene je nekako potaknulo to zapravo moje uključivanje u župu radi hrane.

159
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:34,399
[SPEAKER_01] I to volim baš ispričati, baš radi hrane.

160
00:08:34,639 --> 00:08:36,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vidjela da se tamo jede.

161
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:39,679
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je bilo super.

162
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,480
[SPEAKER_01] Bila je ekipa odlična.

163
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:46,960
